title: TVS Motor joins hands with Emil Frey group to foray into European market
description: TVS Motor Company has officially entered the European market through a significant alliance with the Zurich-based Emil Frey Group. The company announced the formation of an import and distribution pact with Emil Frey, a distinguished 100-year-old enterprise and a prominent name in the automotive distribution sector, according to an official statement.
